title: ISSS608VAA-GROUP15-FINALPROJECT
text:
Welcome to Our Visual Analytics Project
This is the official site for Group 15’s final project for ISSS608 Visual Analytics and Applications based on VAST Challenge 2025 – Mini Challenge 1 (MC1).
Explore how Oceanus Folk spread across the music landscape and discover the next generation of stars with our visual analytics dashboard and supporting content.

title: About Us
text:
We are Group 15 from the ISSS608 Visual Analytics and Applications course at Singapore Management University.
Our project focuses on the VAST Challenge 2025 – MC1: Oceanus Folk Knowledge Graph.




 Rajesh Babu Master of IT in Business


 Pengxin Tan Master of IT in Business


We collaborated to create a meaningful visual analytics solution based on music genre evolution and artist influence.
